title: Joey Bada$$
statement: The Pro Era crew and frontman Joey Bada$$ conclude a cross country tour and prepare for a hometown double headline in New York. [Published on The FADER in 2013.](http://www.thefader.com/2013/05/23/documentary-joey-bada-and-pro-eras-beast-coastal-tour/)
